<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in gilo A hehpih,
 Puk a sesa nung chu;
 Hukdamna bukim lultak chu,
 Man bei in mi A pie'i.

[V2]
 Aw, hehpihna mak ahi,
 Pathien ei hehpihna!
 Ka Hukdampa a hung kumsak,
 Kalvaria thi dingin.

[V3]
 2. Ginna'n Amah kei a ka ti'i,
 Pathien Cha thokit chu;
 A thih ziekin tatna ka mu'i,
 Thisan sawpthienna tawh.

[V4]
 3. Hehpihna'n bukimna a tun,
 Mithiengte A hetsak;
 Lunggil gitloh a sukbei sak,
 Krista mai gin vang in.

[V5]
 4. Gingchate, kipak in chieh u'n,
 Hun na pie ding ahi;
 Lei a na hetlawk uh go thil,
 Van a bei talo ding.

[V6]
 5. Setan nuoisieh a guolzo in,
 Tatsate'n la sau hen;
 Lalpa Krista thihna zal a,
 Guolzo a nunnuom in.</lyrics>
<title>WONDROUS LOVE!</title>
<hymn_number>19</hymn_number>
</song>